{"title":"韶山火种","authors":["李丹平"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"韶山火种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李丹平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年夏天我去韶山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个伟人的旧居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我与万千中外游人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻仰过一盒火柴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那盒火柴敞开着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样子十分普通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火柴盒一侧的磷片已被用过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另一侧却完好如昨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点过纸烟的一盒火柴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在这盒火柴面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我依稀听到了那句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓重的湖南话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——人民的血汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点一滴都要珍惜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在毛泽东众多的遗物当中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这盒火柴似乎最不起眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它却不懈地向人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉说和昭示着什么——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史的荒野上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟人毛泽东分明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是用信念和智慧的火柴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃起熊熊的燎原烈火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧掉了一百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难屈辱的枷锁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了一个民族再生的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和这个民族不屈的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那沉思的纸烟仿佛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧在江山阴霾的季节里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时暗时明……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开那盒火柴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在泥墙青瓦间久久伫立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在苍松翠柏前苦苦思索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那仅仅是一盒火柴吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那仅仅是一个伟人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇高品格的写照吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（那盒火柴里面分明藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一颗不朽的太阳）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而在今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有多少人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少平凡或不平凡的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么需要一盒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的火柴啊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}